{"lemma":"أَوْتارُ","slug":"أَوْتارُ","root":"#.ت.ر","root_slug":"_-ت-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ت-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"وَتَر","root":"وتر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":5,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n41599","n41600","n41601"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to string (as a bow), to provide with a string"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to wrong, to harm, to cheat, to dupe"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to stretch, to strain, to draw tight, to pull taut"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"uneven"},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"odd (numbers)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"string"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sinew, tendon"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"chord"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"hypotenuse"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of وَتَرَ (watara) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew יֶתֶר (yéter, “rope, cord, string, hypotenuse”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41599","headword_ar":"وَتْرٌ","root":"wtr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"witorN","text_ar":"وِتْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n41600","headword_ar":"وِتْرٌ","root":"wtr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"watorN","text_ar":"وَتْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, A, Msb, K, &c.,) the former, [which is the more common,] in the dial. of Nejd, (Lh, M,) and of the tribe of Temeem, (T, S, M, Msb,) and of the people of El-'Áliyeh, (ISk, as on the authority of Yoo, and S) or the latter in the dial. of the people of El-'Áliyeh, (T, as on the authority of Yoo,) or of the people of El-Hijáz, (Lh, S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Single; sole; only; one, and no more:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farodN","text_ar":"فَرْدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, S, M, A, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lamo yu$ofaEo mina AlEadadi","text_ar":"مَا لَمْ يُشْفَعْ مِنَ العَدَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, A, K; except that in the K, instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yu$ofaEo","text_ar":"يُشْفَعْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", we find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yata$af~aEo","text_ar":"يَتَشَفَّعْ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afoEN","text_ar":"شَفْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an odd number:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] all [even and odd] numbers are termed [respectively]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afoEN","text_ar":"شَفْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waitorN","text_ar":"وَِتْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", whether many or few. (T.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"witorFA witorFA","text_ar":"وِتْرًا وِتْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Singly; separately; one by one"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, K.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afoEN","text_ar":"شَفْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwitoru","text_ar":"الوِتْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", one of the names of God,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The Single; the Sole; the One; He who has no equal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like; the Unequalled;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfa*~u","text_ar":"الفَذُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfarodu","text_ar":"الفَرْدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SalaApu Alwaitori","text_ar":"صَلَاةُ الوَِتْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alwitoru","text_ar":"الوِتْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone: see 1, first part: it was sometimes said by Mohammad to be"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rakoEap","text_ar":"رَكْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) ―         -b5-  In the words of the Kur, [lxxxix. 2,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@l$~afoEK","text_ar":"وَا@لشَّفْعٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waA@lowatori","text_ar":"وَا@لْوَتْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"by the former is meant all creatures which are created in pairs; and by the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or [by the former, Adam and his wife; and] by the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Adam,"},{"kind":"text","text":"who was made a pair with his wife: (I' Ab, T:) or by the former, the day of the sacrifice; (T;) and by the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the day of 'Arafeh."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.) (See more voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$afaEN","text_ar":"شَفَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"witorN","text_ar":"وِتْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"watorN","text_ar":"وَتْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, A, Msb, K,) the former, [which is the more common,] in the dial. of Nejd, (Lh, M,) and of the tribe of Temeem, (Lh, T, S, M, Msb,) and of the people of El- 'Áliyeh, (T, as on the authority of Yoo,) and El- Hijáz, (S,) or the latter in the dial. of the people of El-'Aliyeh, (ISk, as on the authority of Yoo, and S) and El-Hijáz, (Lh, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Blood-revenge;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retaliation of murder"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"homicide:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a seeking to revenge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retaliate, blood:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a desire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"seeking, for retaliation of a crime"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of enmity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aHolN","text_ar":"ذَحْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, S, M, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wrongful conduct therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tirapN","text_ar":"تِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"watiyrapN","text_ar":"وَتِيرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", in either sense: (M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a crime which a man commits against another by slaughter"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by plundering"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by capture:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl. [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waitorN","text_ar":"وَِتْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awotaArN","text_ar":"اَوْتَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tirapN","text_ar":"تِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tiraAtN","text_ar":"تِرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (A.)"}],"source_refs":["Lh","M","T","S","Msb","A","K","Mgh","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n41601","headword_ar":"وَتَرٌ","root":"wtr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"string,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"suspensory,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$iroEap","text_ar":"شِرْعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEal~aq","text_ar":"مُعَلَّق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter signifying properly the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appendage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaTama Alqawosa biAlwatari","text_ar":"خَطَمَ القَوْسَ بِالوَتَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nayATN","text_ar":"نَياطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] (M, K,) of a bow: (S, M, Msb, K:) [and in like manner,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a chord"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a lute and the like:] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awotaArN","text_ar":"اَوْتَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"witaArN","text_ar":"وِتَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Fr, Sgh, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"watarapN","text_ar":"وَتَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] in all the senses of the latter. (K.)"}],"source_refs":["M","K","S","Msb"]}]}}